          <div class="maintext">
            (what are the items? when do you need them?)
          </div>
          <div class="subtext">
            Fill us in on the information of the items.
            <br>List the job in the crowdsourcing marketplace.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-3 landingimage">
          <%= image_tag("bid.png", size:"160x150") %>
          <p>Bid</p>
          <div class="maintext">
            (MORE competition, MORE bang for your buck!)
          </div>
          <div class="subtext">
            Shoppers place their bids and compete for your listing in an open and transparent marketplace.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-3 landingimage">
          <%= image_tag("auction4.png", size:"150x150") %>
          <p>Award</p>
          <div class="maintext">
            (Moonlight keeps the "Bounty" aka reward for the Shopper' hard work until the job is done!)
          </div>
          <div class="subtext">
            Review all the bids to make an informed decision.
            <br>*Psst, remember to check the Shoppers' profile and reviews!
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-3 landingimage">
          <%= image_tag("receive3.png", size:"150x150") %>
          <p>Receive</p>
          Sit back, relax and wait for the Shopper to deliver the items to your doorsteps!
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row landingwhat relative">
      <div class="vcenter">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <div class="color-font-s colored">Up to</div>
          <div class="color-font-s">a whopping</div><br>
          <div class="color-font-s colored">50%</div>
